# WHAT WE FED Guardrails

- Preserve project identity from `docs/ai/PROJECT_KERNEL.md`.
- Do not widen into ranch, world-state, kaiju, or unrelated gameplay scope unless explicitly requested.
- Do not reintroduce stale pause-era assumptions.

# Preserve Locked Core

- Timing truth and lane readability are non-negotiable.
- Support readability and telegraph clarity are protected.
- DNA meaning and Bond vs Eat tension remain meaningful.
- No-pause applies during active combat; between-level menus are allowed by design.

# Working Style

- Keep changes surgical and explicit about non-goals.
- Prefer anti-drift decisions over generic optimization.
- Drift harvesting is allowed only in medium/high strategy lanes if guardrails pass.
- Keep implementation/verification lanes bounded by default.
